lead_paragraph: MotoGP world champion Jorge Lorenzo took pole position for the French Grand Prix at Le Mans on Saturday while Yamaha team mate Valentino Rossi struggled and could manage only the third row of the grid.

headline.print_headline: Lorenzo on Pole at Le Mans
